{
  "name": "Sheets",
  "summary": "<p><strong>Sheets</strong> 集合可以包含 <strong>Chart</strong> 或 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Worksheet/Worksheet .htm#Worksheet.Worksheet\">Worksheet</a>**对象。</p>\n<p>如果希望返回所有类型的工作表，<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Sheets/Sheets .htm#Sheets.Sheets\"><strong>Sheets</strong></a> 集合就非常有用。如果仅需使用某一类型的工作表，请参阅该工作表类型的对象主题。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>Sheets</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>Sheets</strong> 集合。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例打印当前活动工作簿上的所有工作表。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PrintOut</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Sheets/Sheets .htm#Sheets.Add\">Add</a>**方法可创建一个新的工作表并将它添加到集合。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例给活动工作簿添加两个图表工作表，将它们放在工作簿中的工作表二之后。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>), <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, xlChart)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong>Sheets</strong>(<em>index</em>)（其中 <em>index</em> 是工作表名称或索引号）可返回一个 <strong>Chart</strong> 或 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Worksheet/Worksheet .htm#Worksheet.Worksheet\">Worksheet</a>**对象。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例激活名为 Sheet1 的工作表。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong>Sheets</strong>(<em>array</em>) 可指定多个工作表。下例将名为“Sheet4”和“Sheet5”的工作表移到工作簿的开头。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将名为 Sheet4 和 Sheet5 的工作表移动到工作簿的开头。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>([<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet4&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet5&quot;</span>]).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Move</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>指定的或活动工作簿中所有工作表的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)\n{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>){\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>{\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作簿中的工作表数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例判断如果当前工作簿成功添加一个工作表，则显示结果。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> count = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ThisWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ThisWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ThisWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> == count + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;成功添加一个工作表&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "HPageBreaks",
      "summary": "<p>每张工作表最多有 1026 个水平分页符。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/HPageBreaks/HPageBreaks .htm#HPageBreaks.HPageBreaks\">HPageBreaks</a>**集合，它代表工作表上的水平分页符。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示全屏水平分页符和打印区水平分页符的个数。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cFull = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cPartial = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Extent</span> == xlPageBreakFull) {\n            ++cFull\n        } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n            ++cPartial\n        }\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(cFull + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot; full-screen page breaks, &quot;</span> + cPartial + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot; print-area page breaks&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作簿中索引为1和2的工作表的水平分页符类型是否是手动插入分页符。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> array = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> type = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(array).<span class=\"hljs-property\">HPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(type == xlPageBreakManual)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "HPageBreaks",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "VPageBreaks",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/VPageBreaks/VPageBreaks .htm#VPageBreaks.VPageBreaks\">VPageBreaks</a>**集合，它代表工作表上的垂直分页符。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示全屏垂直分页符和打印区垂直分页符的个数。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cFull = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cPartial = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">VPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">VPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Extent</span> == xlPageBreakFull) {\n            ++cFull\n        } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n            ++cPartial\n        }\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(cFull + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot; full-screen page breaks, &quot;</span> + cPartial + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot; print-area page breaks&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作簿中索引为1和2的工作表的垂直分页符类型是否是手动插入分页符。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> array = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> type = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(array).<span class=\"hljs-property\">VPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(type == xlPageBreakManual)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "VPageBreaks",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Visible",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Variant</strong> 值，它确定对象是否可见。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将名称为“Sheet2”和“Sheet3”的工作表设置为不可见。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> names = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet2&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet3&quot;</span>]\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(names).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = msoFalse\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将活动工作簿中索引为1和2的工作表设置为可见。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> names = [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(names).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = msoTrue\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Add",
      "summary": "<p>如果同时省略 <em>Before</em> 和 <em>After</em>，则新工作表插入到活动工作表之前。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>新建工作表、图表或宏表。新建的工作表将成为活动工作表。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将新建工作表插入到活动工作簿的最后一张工作表之前。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作簿中的最后一个工作表之后插入一个新图表，并将返回的对象赋值sheet变量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>), <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, xlChart)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Before",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>指定工作表的对象，新建的工作表将置于此工作表之前。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "After",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>指定工作表的对象，新建的工作表将置于此工作表之后。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Count",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>要添加的工作表数。默认值为 1。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Type",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>指定工作表类型。可以为下列 XlSheetType 常量之一：xlWorksheet、xlChart、xlExcel4MacroSheet 或 xlExcel4IntlMacroSheet。如果基于现有模板插入工作表，则指定该模板的路径。默认值为 xlWorksheet。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>一个 Object 值，它代表新的工作表、图表或宏表。</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "name": "Copy",
      "summary": "<p>如果既不指定 <em>Before</em> 也不指定 <em>After</em>，则 ET 将新建一个工作簿，其中包含复制的工作表。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>将工作表复制到工作簿的另一位置。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例复制工作表 Sheet1，并将其放置在工作表 Sheet3 之前。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Copy</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet3&quot;</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例复制工作表 Sheet1，并将其放置在工作表 Sheet3 之后。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Copy</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet3&quot;</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Before",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>将要在其之前放置所复制工作表的工作表。如果指定了 After，则不能指定 Before。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "After",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>将要在其之后放置所复制工作表的工作表。如果指定了 Before，则不能指定 After。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例删除活动工作簿中名称为“Sheet1”和“Sheet2”工作表。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> names = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet2&quot;</span>]\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(names).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例删除索引为2和3的工作表。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>([<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>]).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
